# Fact Sheet: Content Factory (SYS-CONTENT)

[content/generation]
F-001: The system shall generate four assets per topic: Research Pack, YouTube Script, Blog Article, and Thumbnail Prompts. @spec
F-002: Programmatic assets must be uploaded to S3-compatible storage with unique hash IDs. @spec @db
F-003: Video narrations must be generated using ElevenLabs API and stored in S3. @spec

[content/governance]
F-004: Content status must follow workflow: DRAFT ➔ UNDER_REVIEW ➔ APPROVED ➔ PUBLISHED. @spec @db
F-005: Every content asset must require manual Human Editor approval before status changes to APPROVED. @spec @ui
F-006: Asset metadata must reference active licenses for all Envato/Stock elements. @spec @db
